text: Yoshitaka Takeda (15 February 1911 - 1943) was a Japanese gymnast. He competed at the 1932 Summer Olympics and the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:1943 deaths Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ehime Prefecture
